          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">DPD</ENAMEX> entries lie <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">more than 10 bp</NUMEX> upstream, and in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">11</TIMEX>
          cases, a newly derived putative <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">TSS</ENAMEX> was <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">more than 10</NUMEX> bp
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">5</ENAMEX>' of the corresponding <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">TSS</ENAMEX> in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">DPD</ENAMEX>. Of the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">205</NUMEX> core
          promoter regions in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CPD</ENAMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">32</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">sites</ENAMEX> (<NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">16%</NUMEX>) belonging to
          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">30</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">genes</ENAMEX> could be aligned successfully; in <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">21</NUMEX> out of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">30</NUMEX>
          cases, the difference was again smaller than <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">10 bp</TIMEX>, in
