          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">sensitivity</ENAMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">82%</NUMEX> of the true predictions by McPromoter
          are located within <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CpG</ENAMEX> islands, and the correlation gets
          stronger as the specificity increases. This was also
          reported for other, more recently developed
